#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If the port installs a shell script whose purpose is to launch another "
"program, and if launching that program is the last action performed by the "
"script, make sure to launch the program using the `exec` statement, for "
"instance:"
msgstr ""
"Si el puerto instala un script de shell cuyo propósito es iniciar otro "
"programa, y si el lanzamiento de ese programa es la última acción realizada "
"por el script, asegúrese de iniciar el programa utilizando el "
"<function>exec</function> declaración, por ejemplo:"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/porting-dads/_index.adoc:168
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"#!/bin/sh\n"
